name: "Tripping the Light Fantastic" CD (2009)
description:
Born and raised by wolves in the Dirty Jersey, Sir Tofur is here to shake things up a bit. Combining elements of glitch electronic, underground hip-hop, and radio friendly pop, 'Tripping the Light Fantastic' serves as a great introduction to the one, the only, Sir Tofur, as he weaves his way through a lengthy laundry list of genres and influences. 2009 Rub One Out Records.

Track listing:

1. beatSelektor Theme (1:31)
2. What You Deserve (4:47)
3. Pull Back! Aim! Reclaim! (4:16)
4. No Hard Feelings (1:41)
5. Solomon's Tale (3:54)
6. I Could (3:54)
7. The Original (Interlude) (0:44)
8. outMIX.1 (3:36)
9. Unrelenting Confusion as a State of Existence (2:33)
10. North Atlantic Blues (4:13)
11. Inspired (2:00)

14. What You Deserve (acoustic remix) (4:26)


All songs written, performed, recorded, edited, and produced by Topher Hendricks.
